# Create a release branch from trunk\nsvn copy http://your-svn-url/trunk http://your-svn-url/branches/release-1.0 -m "Creating 1.0 release branch"\n\n# Developers check out this branch for bug fixes:\nsvn checkout http://your-svn-url/branches/release-1.0\n\n# Once all bugs are fixed and tested, you can tag the release:\nsvn copy http://your-svn-url/branches/release-1.0 http://your-svn-url/tags/release-1.0 -m "Tagging 1.0 release"\n\n# After tagging, consider merging fixes back to trunk if needed.